'''[[Mali]]''' (MLI) has sent athletes to [[Summer Olympic Games]] held in [[1964 Summer Olympics|1964]], [[1972 Summer Olympics|1972]], and every other Olympics since [[1980 Summer Olympics|1980]], although the country has never won an [[Olympic Games#Olympic champions and medalists|Olympic medal]].  No athletes from Mali have competed in any [[Winter Olympic Games]].

